## Common Mistakes to Avoid
- Don’t put secrets in repo; use .env (e.g. YETIMATCH_API_KEY) and keep .env gitignored
- Don’t assume platform APIs without Platform.isXXX or conditional imports
- Don’t forget to add new assets under `flutter.assets` in pubspec.yaml
